            "title": "日本最大銀行擬延長退休年齡 在人口老齡化壓力下留住人才",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"日本最大銀行擬延長退休年齡 在人口老齡化壓力下留住人才\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qq46VbprP2NkC34uLH9xug--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/e46befa0-2836-11f1-97fa-e789ad28798e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">日本最大銀行擬延長退休年齡 在人口老齡化壓力下留住人才</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
